      "text": "In 158 AG, the Agni Kai Triad broke into the Sato estate.\u00a0During the robbery, one of the members killed Yasuko, Hiroshi Sato's wife, an event that caused Hiroshi to develop a deep hatred for all benders and eventually join the Equalists."
