    {
      "body": "When Mako and Korra approached ${link_0} in ${link_1} for information regarding ${link_2}'s whereabouts, he mentioned that all the gangs, including the Agni Kai Triad, the Triple Threats, and the Red Monsoons, were recruiting extra muscle for something big.",
